getProtocolInfo

public ClientStub.Info getProtocolInfo()
从类 ClientStub 复制的描述
Meta-information about the protocol that this stub uses to talk to external clients. This is sent to the client as a part of the handshake.

指定者：
类 ClientStub 中的 getProtocolInfo

eventWrapperFromBytes

public EventWrapper eventWrapperFromBytes(byte[] v)
从类 ClientStub 复制的描述
Convert an array of bytes into an event wrapper. This method is used to translate data received from a client into events that may be injected into the S4 cluster.

指定者：
类 ClientStub 中的 eventWrapperFromBytes
参数：
v - array of bytes
返回：
EventWrapper constructed from the byte array.

bytesFromEventWrapper

public byte[] bytesFromEventWrapper(EventWrapper ew)
从类 ClientStub 复制的描述
Convert an event wrapper into a byte array. Events received from the S4 cluster for dispatching to a client are translated into a byte array using this method.

指定者：
类 ClientStub 中的 bytesFromEventWrapper
参数：
ew - an EventWrapper
返回：
a byte array
